Subject: Secunia Research: libsndfile "aiff_read_chanmap()" Information Disclosure Vulnerability

======================================================================

                    Secunia Research 2017/06/09
                                            
libsndfile "aiff_read_chanmap()" Information Disclosure Vulnerability

======================================================================
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
